(5583, 261, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', NULL, 'Global Supply Chain Management (AEC)?', NULL, NULL, '2 Years', NULL, NULL, 1, 'The Global Supply Chain Management (AEC) is designed for students interested in pursuing an exciting career in Supply Chain Management. This program has been designed as a response to the growing demandfor Supply Chain and Logistics professionals by the business community in and around Montreal and globally.?The program offers insights into the domains linked to Supply Chain Management, Inventory Management, Warehouse Management, International Procurement, Marketing & Distribution.  As business in Transportation, Logistics and Supply Chain are using Information Technology as an enabler to run their operations smoothly, we have integrated an IT component into the program to ensure that our students have well-rounded skills that would help them get hired and contribute effectively in a dynamic work environment.', NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL),
(5584, 261, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', NULL, 'Civil Engineering Technology - Design and Testing ACS', NULL, NULL, '2 Years', NULL, NULL, 1, 'There is a high demand in global as well as Canadian Civil Engineering job market for skilled employees who have multiple skill sets in the areas of drafting, design and material testing. Matrix College?s AEC in Civil Engineering Technology ? Design and Material Testing is aligned to meet this market requirement and prepare Civil Engineering technicians who are able to design pieces of building structures, supervise sites and test construction materials thereby becoming usefull assistants to Civil Engineers, Project Managers and Architects. This program makes you job ready for positions in Civil Engineering firms, Construction Materials Suppliers, Construction and Project Management companies.', NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL),
(5585, 261, NULL, NULL, 'NA', '', '$12,334.00 CAD', NULL, 'Computer Science Technology - Software Testing', NULL, NULL, '2 Years', NULL, NULL, 1, 'There is tremendous demand for qualified IT professionals globally and in Canada. Potential employers are seeking skilled employees who have specialized software testing abilities coupled with knowledge of operating systems, databases and programming.?Coll?ge de gestion, technologie et sant? Matrix inc. / Matrix college of Mangament, Technology and Healthcare Inc AEC in Computer Science Technology Software Testing prepares you to be a Computer Science Technician who is capable of understanding business requirements, writing test cases, testing applications, products and solutions using functional and automated testing methods. This program opens up job opportunities for you across banking, insurance, health and manufacturing domain.', NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL),
