(2, 1, 'Leadership', 'Meet the founders of University Bureau, with their collective experience of more than a century and expertise in higher education, technology, security, engineering, HR, finance, customer success, and more; led the foundation of University Bureau.', '<p>Meet the founders of University Bureau, with their collective experience of more than a century and expertise in higher education, technology, security, engineering, HR, finance, customer success, and more; led the foundation of <strong>University Bureau.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Founders <strong>Mr. DP Chaudhary</strong> and <strong>Mr. Rajan Arya</strong> are the two main pillars that laid the foundation of the University Bureau; these two are exceptionally and distinctively talented and masters of their respective fields.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mr. DP. Chaudhary</strong> is an expert of the international education system, having more than 16 years of experience dedicatedly in the industry of overseas education. He started to embellish student&#39;s careers with Rite Education Private Limited and has delivered extraordinary values for the overseas education industry since 2005.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mr. Rajan Arya</strong>, an Author, Blogger, and present Chief Digital Officer and Chief Executive Officer of Info Birth Innovations Pvt Ltd. &amp; Info Birth Innovations INC, has experience of more than 13 years in delivering optimal results &amp; business value via Data Science / Digital Marketing Solutions. He conceptualized, developed, and led many new knowledge analytics-based capabilities which have had far-reaching industry impact. He is passionate about Digital Marketing, Digital Transformation, Product Development /Marketing. Before Infobirth Innovations Pvt Ltd. &amp; Infobirth Innovations INC, Rajan has held several top management positions. He has worked with Investors Clinic Infratech Ltd &amp; Motion Infotech Pvt. Ltd. as Chief Digital Officer, Armada Group (Kuwait) as Head of Digital Marketing team, RBS (Royal Bank Of Scotland) as Analyst &ndash; Rmo, Option Town Softwares Inc as Head of Digital Marketing. He is Google Ads, Tableau, Salesforce, HubSpot &amp; ITIL V4, RPA Certified.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Together, they sowed the seed of the University Bureau. Combining the expertise of both, University Bureau delivers exceptional services to our partner institutions. It helps them in recruiting quality candidates and streamlining their admission.</p>\r\n', '', 'leadership', '', '', 'ACTIVE', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(3, 1, 'Shape the Future of International Student Recruitment', 'University Bureau aims to educate the world by providing a platform where anyone from anywhere has access to the best education.\r\n\r\nWe believe in \"Education is the passport to the future, for tomorrow belongs to those who prepare for it today.\" Malcolm X.\r\n\r\n', '<p>Why join University Bureau? &bull; Be a part of our mission to spread education and help students get the best education. &bull; We enhance the team&#39;s entrepreneurial spirit and be at the side to help you grow, move fast, be a resourceful team member of the organization, and create your magic. &bull; We believe in growing together, keeping the team a vital organizational resource. &bull; We work 24x7 but never forget to celebrate the win, birthday, special day, festivals with full enthusiasm. &bull; We have a team from problem solvers to builders to connectors worldwide, which will help you raise the bar. &bull; We have a team in the USA, separated by geography but working as one. &bull; We provide our employees an Employee and Family Assistance Program for health and wellness benefits. &bull; We give our fellow team members access to technology, training, and resources needed for a great onboarding experience. University bureau values: &bull; Freedom to do what you say to achieve the goal. &bull; Give your best shot of work. &bull; Support to win and celebrate; in downfall, we will patt your back and help to win. &bull; Help students to achieve their success. &bull; Treat team members as family and respect their decisions. &bull; We work with 100% honesty and with good intent. &bull; Target to give A+ customer experience. &bull; Innovate and improve with time. Current Openings Join the University Bureau and move on a mission with us to empower people worldwide to get access to the best education. Location: Division ACCOUNT MANAGER FONTANA, CA &ndash; SALES APPLY NOW MANAGER GLOBAL ADMISSION INDIA (Noida) &ndash; ADMISSIONS APPLY NOW CUSTOMER SUPPORT eXecutive INDIA (Noida) &ndash; OPERATIONS APPLY NOW CAMPAIGN MANAGER INDIA (Noida) &ndash; MARKETING APPLY NOW CONTENT COORDINATOR FONTANA, CA &ndash; SALES APPLY NOW CONTENT MANAGER FONTANA, CA &ndash; SALES APPLY NOW CRM SPECIALIST SRI LANKA &ndash; MARKETING APPLY NOW CUSTOMER SUPPORT OFFICER INDIA (Noida) &ndash; CUSTOMER SUCCESS APPLY NOW PAYROLL MANAGER INDIA (Noida) &ndash; FINANCE APPLY NOW PROCESSING OFFICER INDIA (Noida) &ndash; ADMISSIONS APPLY NOW QCV OFFICER INDIA (Noida) &ndash; ADMISSIONS APPLY NOW TRAINING OFFICER &ndash; NORTH ASIA INDIA (Noida) &ndash; TRAINING &amp; DEVELOPMENT DIVISION APPLY NOW VISA-SERVICES OFFICER INDIA (Noida) &ndash; ADMISSIONS APPLY NOW Enquire Now Button like: ( ) Page will direct to: General Enquiry (Form) First Name* Last Name* E-mail* Role* Office* Resume / CV (PDF Only) * Message* Our Ofes Subscribe us If you wish to receive e-mails about the people &amp; stories behind the platform, subscribe to us.</p>\r\n', '', 'carrer-info', '', '', 'ACTIVE', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(4, 1, 'FAQ', '', '<p>1.What exactly is University Bureau about? University Bureau is an online recruitment platform, which aim to empower students and create solutions for tomorrow&rsquo;s challenges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.How does University Bureau work? Team of University Bureau guide, build confidence, help students across the world to study and get the best international education. We provide a recruitment platform which enables institutions and recruitment agents to find and transact with each other, seamlessly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.How platform which University Bureau is a time saving recruitment tool? Platform which University Bureau provides, makes the search easy for students, institutions and recruiters to study abroad, fill application, and makes the acceptance process successful by connecting international students, recruitment partners (5,000+), and academic institutions (1,500+) on one platform across Canada, the United States, the United Kingdom, and Australia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.What is the role of Quality Compliance and Visa (QCV) team? Quality Compliance and Visa (QCV) team conduct in-depth checks on all visa and course applications by using intuitive automation tools before sending to recruiters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.How the data submitted by students/recruiter is organised? The data of each student is organised in one secure place by following a Privacy compliance program aligned with the General Data Protection Regulation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.How University Bureau helps students? University Bureau work hard to make the dream of students to come true by helping them to apply to institutes or programs based on their skills and interest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7.How University Bureau helps recruiters? University Bureau provide a trusted platform to recruiters which help students to do their best and fulfill their dream to study internationally.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Students</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.Why to choose University Bureau? Choose University Bureau for the best assistance to discover programs and institutions, get the best options for you, and prepare everything for easy submission of your applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.What features does University Bureau offers to students? University Bureau provides:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Admission officer: Select your admission officer from our platform and get guidance from creating your profile to applying to multiple institutions and course selection from over 50,000+ programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; IELETS trainer: We have a team of the world&rsquo;s best trainers from where you can select your trainer by using our platform to prepare yourself for the IELTS exam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Financial officer: Our financial officers will provide you with exclusive scholarships and good financial support options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Visa Assistance: Our top-rated certified visa counselor will help you at every step of the visa process, from application filing to document preparation. You can select a top-rated counselor at your convenience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Continuous Support: We have a team of over 5,000+ recruiters, certified experts for 1-on-1 support around the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.How University Bureau works? University Bureau built a relationship with students on Trust and Credibility. UB will take a short survey, filter &amp; select programs and institute for students. Then University Bureau will help students to complete their profile, pay fees, and submit documents. Once the institute reviews student&rsquo;s application and issues an acceptance letter then our expert recruiter will guide you through the visa application process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Institutions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.How University Bureau helps institutions? University Bureau connects qualified students and recruiters on a single, easy-to-use platform, which is trusted by more than 1500+ Institutions worldwide. University Bureau train recruitment partners through an industry specialist to ensure that they&rsquo;re ready to promote the institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.How University Bureau is an internationally recognised and trusted globally? University Bureau team of experts understands the unique challenges which institute face and makes you stand out from the rest- by working with you at every step of the way. We assure you to deliver the quality and compliance checks in the industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>For Recruiters</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.How University Bureau support institutions? Access University Bureau recruitment platform to get a variety of exclusive bonuses and to give a boost to your earnings. University Bureau gives you a network of 1,500+ institutions worldwide, and advanced filtering tools to find the best options for your student.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.How University Bureau is different from other websites?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Use University Bureau recruitment platform to process applications faster than ever and make your students happy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; By working with University Bureau you can lodged your application within 3 hours and use only one form to apply in multiple institutes with a maximum success rate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; You can get instant updates from our global admission experts based on your application to enhance the chances of getting selected in the institutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; All the documents are organised by using Document manager which uploads each application in seconds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.How much commision does University Bureau gives to its recruiters? University Bureau will give ou upto 100% commission which an institution pays for successful student placement.</p>\r\n', '', 'faq', '', '', 'ACTIVE', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5, 1, 'Our Story', '', '<p>Overseas education and have the capability of counseling students and suggesting them the right institutions as per their academic interests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What does University Bureau offer:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; An online recruitment AI-enabled platform for institutions, students, and recruiters to connect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Complete CRM solutions along with comprehensive digital solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>To Students:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Admission guidance from selecting their admission officer to creating a profile to applying to multiple institutions and course selection from over 50,000+ programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Choose the world&#39;s best IELTS trainers from our platform and prepare for the IELTS exam.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Top-rated certified visa officers to help in the visa process, from application filing to document preparation. Here also, they can select top-rated officers and get guidance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Online support to queries by our certified experts &bull;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To Recruiters:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Access our recruitment platform to select students and institutions and guide them through the process by giving them support locally or globally using our online support system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Process applications faster than ever and make your students happy. Lodged their application within 3 hours and use only one form to apply in multiple institutes with a maximum success rate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Get instant updates from our global admission experts based on the application to enhance the chances of getting selected.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Document manager to store the documents and upload each application in seconds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Customer Relationship Officers and Regional Managers to help you with anything you need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Training sessions by our institution specialists to keep you informed about the entry requirement to the institution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>To Institutions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Our team of experts understands the unique challenges faced by institutions and makes you stand out from the rest- by working with you at every step of the way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Skilled people and leading technology, to get the most accurate processing systems in international education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Get quality students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Reach over 5,000+ recruiters in key and emerging source markets.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Our experts will provide you an automatic tool to check incomplete or fraudulent applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Quality Compliance and Visa (QCV) team to conducts in-depth checks on all visa and course applications before they&#39;re sent to you. University Bureau helps students to make confident study decisions by providing them a trusted marketplace using intelligent technology which connects the world&#39;s institutions, recruiters &amp; service providers.</p>\r\n', '', 'our-story', '', '', 'ACTIVE', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6, 1, ' Privacy and Cookies Policy', '', '<p><strong>Last Updated: April 20, 2022</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>University Bureau guides users to know the process of studying overses to Student, how to become our Recruiter partner around the world, including information about visa applications and programs. UB also provides the guidance to apply for admission to specific institutions&#39; programs through our recruitment partners, admission officers, and our Website to begin the journey as an international student.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To do this, University Bureau collects your data. This Privacy &amp; Cookies Policy sets out how University Bureau collects, uses, discloses, and manages personal data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: The changes we made to this Policy go from time to time and get updated with the date listed above. Your continued use of the University Bureau&#39;s services and Website will be subject to our updated Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>This Policy describes:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The information which we collect and process as provided by you directly or by third parties (recruitment partners and counselors).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The purposes of collecting and processing information about you is to procees your application successfully.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the basis on which we collect and process information about you when you use the Website https://universitybureau.com/ (our &quot;<strong>Website</strong>&quot;) and the services available through this Website, is provided to our registered users (our &quot;<strong>Services</strong>&quot;).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this Policy, the term &quot;<strong>Personal Data</strong>&quot; or &quot;<strong>Personal Information</strong>&quot; means personal data or data that is related to an identified or identifiable person.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UB recommends you to read this Policy carefully and understand what University Bureau and any affiliates and subsidiaries do with your data. When you use our Website and Services, in case of any dispute over privacy, it is subjected to this Policy and any of our applicable Terms and Conditions for our Services. Our Terms and Conditions for you are incorporated by reference into this Policy. By visiting our Website, you are accepting the terms and conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>How university bureau collect and process data</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>University Bureau collect personal data directly from you or from third parties such as our marketing affiliates, banking references, credit reporting agencies, affiliates, website hosts, live chat, and online support service providers to verify your identity and prevent any fraudulent activity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>University bureau provides its users, clients, or customers services as part of a customer referral program, through cookies and metadata collected through our Website and the Services. At this time, the use of our Services is only available to users who register for our Services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>We, and our third-party service providers, automatically collect the information such as:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Domain name</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browser type&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating system</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Web pages you view</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Links you click</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IP address</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Length of time you visit our website or use our Services</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Activities on our Website</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Referring URL or the webpage that led you to our Website.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through cookies, web beacons, log files, and other technologies by applicable law.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>What personal data does&nbsp;</strong><strong>the university bureau</strong>&nbsp;<strong>collect?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The types of personal data UB collect about you depend on your interaction with our Website and our Services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For example,Suppose you view the application process of specific institutions. For this:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ub need to collect sensitive personal data revealing racial or ethnic origin, political opinions, religious or philosophical beliefs, trade union membership, genetic or biometric data, health information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note: </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We collect any sensitive data about you if it is necessary, and for that we will follow data protection laws and take your explicit consent to do so.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The personal data collected from you will only be shared with the university bureau and our third-party service providers acting as data processors to provide the Services requested by you. They will not be transferred or used by us for any other purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Below are the categories of personal data, which the University Bureau collect about you, where permitted by applicable law:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Type of Personal Data UB ask</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Source of Personal Data</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Name, date of birth, email address, IP address, phone number, billing address.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Directly from you, third parties on your behalf and as instructed by you, other University Bureau users and customers, our service providers and affiliates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Financial information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Health information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Information collected through Cookies</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From you directly and our third party analytic tools and cookies usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Geolocation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Contact information, professional credentials, education, work history, salary, evaluations, references, interviews, certifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Directly from you, third parties on your behalf and as instructed or permitted by you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any other information which you choose to provide to us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When UB Collect and use Your Information</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UB collect your personal data whenever you:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Create an Account:</strong>&nbsp;To access certain features present on the Website, you are required to create an account, by providing email address and password or you can sign in with Facebook or Google. Your login information is used to create your account.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Explore what programs you are eligible to apply to:</strong>&nbsp;You do not have to create an account to visit and browse certain features of our Website, such as to browse various institutions and programs, read other content portions of the Website, or to know your eligibility for certain programs. If you choose to use our Website to discover programs you are eligible to apply for, we collect personal data (nationality, country of education, highest education, grading scheme, grade average, IELTS exam score(s) ) and the disciplines or programs that you are interested in pursuing. University Bureau uses this information to create a list of programs and institutions to which you are eligible to apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Create a Student Profile and/or Apply to an Educational Program:</strong>&nbsp;To apply for any educational program, student, recruitment partner, councellor&nbsp; are required to create a student profile on our Website. The personal data which we collect through student profile will helps us to match you with institutions and programs that fit your preferences and qualifications. The information may include your first and last name, email address, gender, date of birth, home and mailing address, passport details, marital status, emergency contact information, English or language test score(s), educational preferences, education history, volunteer experience, and other educational information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Throughout the application process, you need to provide additional information as required such as documentation of awards and school projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: This information is not required to process your application but it will enhance the success of your application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We may use your profile information and other information about your use of the Website&nbsp; to provide you with tailored school recommendations through the Website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Email Account:</strong>&nbsp;We will create and provide you with an &ldquo;University Bureau&rdquo; email account to facilitate your communications with certain institutes of interest. University Bureau email accounts are only used for applying to educational programs through University Bureau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Use of Our Services for Visa Processing:</strong>&nbsp;We offer students the option of processing their student visas or selecting their Visa officers through University Bureau. If you choose to use this service, University Bureau may collect your personal data for the purposes of processing your visa application, passport details and information included on a visa application form.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Post On Our Website or Social Media Channels:</strong>&nbsp;You have the ability to post information (e.g. questions, comments and opinions) through University Bureau services or on social media platforms, such as Facebook, LinkedIn, or Instagram, as well as send us direct messages via these platforms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Any personal data which you voluntarily post to any public forum will be available to other individuals and you should exercise caution when posting any personal data. The content which you post on sites owned by third parties is subjected to the privacy policies of those third parties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Register to Take Any Courses:</strong>&nbsp;You will have the ability to access our course content and provide voluntary personal data to register you as an individual for applying the course. We will keep a record of you details which you have used during registration process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Interact with Live Chat and Online Support Services:</strong>&nbsp;We provide online support services powered by third parties on our Website to provide additional information or answer any questions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your information (your first and last name, phone number, email address, IP address, and other data communicated while using the support services) is collected with the aim of operating the online support services and analyzing the use of those services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note: Live chat conversations &nbsp;or telephonic conversation may also be logged for quality assurance and training purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By using the support services on our Website, you are giving us the consent of collecting and using your information. You are solely responsible for the information you choose to submit while using the support services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Communicate with Us:</strong>&nbsp;When you contact us with a comment, question or complaint, you may be asked for the information (name, address and a phone number) to help us to promptly answer your question or respond to your comment or complaint.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> We may also retain this information to assist you in the future and to improve our customer service, products, service offerings, events and promotions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Provide Information to Third Parties With Whom We Work:</strong>&nbsp;University Bureau may obtain personal data about you through your legal representative, or a recruitment partner(s) or counsellor(s) who you are working with us and are using our services to process your application to institutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Payment Processing and Transaction Tracking:</strong>&nbsp;University Bureau with your consent, uses third party PCI certified payment service providers including but not limited to Western Union, Flywire or Stripe. When you directly make a payment by using these payment service providers, you are subject to their privacy policies. They are independent of University Bureau.</p>\r\n', '', 'privacy-and-cookies-policy', '', '', 'ACTIVE', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `pages` (`id`, `author_id`, `title`, `excerpt`, `body`, `image`, `slug`, `meta_description`, `meta_keywords`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(7, 1, 'Terms And Conditions', '', '<p>The Terms and Conditions, including the Privacy Policy, are a legal contract between you and the University Bureau that governs your use of the Services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>YOU AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF THIS AGREEMENT BY CLICKING ON THE APPROPRIATE BUTTON WHEN SIGNING UP FOR THE SERVICES AND BY USING THE SERVICES.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>YOU WILL NOT BE ALLOWED TO USE THE UNIVERSITY BUREAU IF YOU DO NOT ACCEPT AND AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THE AGREEMENT.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Except where prohibited by law, University Bureau has the right to amend the terms and conditions by posting a new version on the University Bureau website. If you continue to use or access the University Bureau after any modifications to the Agreement, you agree to them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can contact us at support@universitybureau.com if you have any questions or issues concerning this Agreement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>In these Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Applicable Law&quot; refers to any domestic or foreign law, rule, statute, subordinate legislation, regulation, bylaw, order, ordinance, protocol, code, guideline, treaty, policy, notice, direction, or judicial, arbitral, administrative, ministerial, or departmental judgment, award, decree, treaty, directive, or other requirement or guideline published or in force at any time during the term of this Agreement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any rule, order, judgment, directive, or other requirement or guideline issued by any Governmental or Regulatory Authority relates to or is otherwise intended to govern or regulate any person (including any Party), property, transaction, activity, event, or another thing. &ldquo;University Bureau Partner&rdquo; means any educational institution, company, organization, association, or individual that has agreed with University Bureau to use or promote the University Bureau or enable their employees or students to use it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>University Bureau website and Services and the Content contained therein, as they may be amended from time to time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Confidential Information&quot; includes the University Bureau, its business plan and strategy, any design, prototype, a compilation of information, data, program, method, invention, license, technique or process, information relating to any University Bureau service, University Bureau&#39;s software, website and web platform, client and user information, financial information, marketing information, and information relating to any University Bureau service.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Governmental or Regulatory Authority&quot; means any national, provincial, territorial, state, country, municipal, quasi-governmental, or self-regulatory department, authority, organization, agency, commission, board, tribunal, dispute re panel or body, bureau, official, minister, Crown corporation, or court or other law, rule, or regulation-making entity having or purporting to have jurisdiction over University Bureau, you, or any other person, property, transaction, or other matter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Party&quot; refers to each of the University Bureau and you individually, and &quot;Parties&quot; refers to the University Bureau and you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Personal Information&quot; refers to information concerning a specific person.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Program&quot; refers to a study program, language program, or summer camp offered by the University Bureau Partners and one of the academic programs or a program specifically tailored to transition international students (often referred to as a route program).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Recruiter&quot; refers to any person or 